<div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)\"><main><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-white\"><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0F1A14] via-[#1A3A2E] to-[#2D6A4F] pt-28 pb-16\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#95D5B2] hover:text-white mb-10 transition-colors\" href=\"/portfolio\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m12 19-7-7 7-7\"></path><path d=\"M19 12H5\"></path></svg> Back to Portfolio</a><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start gap-6\"><div class=\"h-16 w-16 rounded-2xl bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm flex items-center justify-center text-[#95D5B2] shrink-0 border border-white/20\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-recycle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M7 19H4.815a1.83 1.83 0 0 1-1.57-.881 1.785 1.785 0 0 1-.004-1.784L7.196 9.5\"></path><path d=\"M11 19h8.203a1.83 1.83 0 0 0 1.556-.89 1.784 1.784 0 0 0 0-1.775l-1.226-2.12\"></path><path d=\"m14 16-3 3 3 3\"></path><path d=\"M8.293 13.596 7.196 9.5 3.1 10.598\"></path><path d=\"m9.344 5.811 1.093-1.892A1.83 1.83 0 0 1 11.985 3a1.784 1.784 0 0 1 1.546.888l3.943 6.843\"></path><path d=\"m13.378 9.633 4.096 1.098 1.097-4.096\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full border bg-amber-50 text-amber-700 border-amber-200\">Circular Economy</span><span class=\"text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full border bg-purple-50 text-purple-700 border-purple-200\">Pre-Seed</span></div><h1 class=\"font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-white mb-4 leading-tight\">C-link</h1><a href=\"https://c-link.world\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-[#95D5B2] hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium\">Visit website <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-external-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 3h6v6\"></path><path d=\"M10 14 21 3\"></path><path d=\"M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-2\"><h2 class=\"font-serif text-2xl text-[#1A3A2E] mb-5\">About <!-- -->C-link</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">What C-Link Does</p><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">C-Link transforms organic waste streams into verified carbon removal and agricultural products through Terrestrial Storage. Our facilities process municipal biosolids, green waste, agricultural residues, and disaster debris—materials that traditionally create methane emissions, fire hazards, and disposal costs—and convert them into stable carbon storage and regenerative soil inputs.</p></div><h2 class=\"font-serif text-2xl text-[#1A3A2E] mt-8 mb-3\">Our Investment Thesis</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"font-serif text-2xl text-[#1A3A2E] mt-6\">What C-Link Does</h2><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">C-Link transforms organic waste streams into verified carbon removal and agricultural products through Terrestrial Storage. Our facilities process municipal biosolids, green waste, agricultural residues, and disaster debris—materials that traditionally create methane emissions, fire hazards, and disposal costs—and convert them into stable carbon storage and regenerative soil inputs.</p><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">Each ton of material processed generates independently verified Carbon Removal Certificates (CORCs) representing permanent CO2 removal, plus nutrient-rich growing media for agricultural markets. This dual-output model addresses converging needs in waste management, climate accountability, and soil regeneration.</p><h2 class=\"font-serif text-2xl text-[#1A3A2E] mt-6\">The Technology: MicroSnap Process</h2><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">C-Link&#x27;s Terrestrial Storage utilizes MicroSnap&#x27;s carbon preservation technology—an advanced microbial process that stabilizes organic carbon at ambient temperature through controlled biological activity.</p><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg text-[#1A3A2E] mt-4\">Verified Performance Metrics:</h3><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\"><strong>Energy efficiency</strong></p><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">Produces biochar-equivalent carbon storage using approximately one-tenth the energy of thermal pyrolysis</p><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\"><strong>Mass retention</strong></p><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">Preserves 95-97% of starting material mass, maximizing both carbon capture and product yield</p><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\"><strong>Processing time</strong></p><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">Completes stabilization in 14-60 days versus 6-12 months for traditional composting</p><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\"><strong>Storage stability</strong></p><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">Independently verified to 100-year permanence standards</p><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">Safety Advantages: Ambient-temperature processing eliminates fire risks inherent in thermal composting and pyrolysis operations. This reduces insurance costs and enables deployment in urban and suburban contexts where thermal operations face regulatory barriers.</p><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">Pathogen and Contaminant Elimination: Third-party testing confirms complete destruction of pathogens including fecal coliforms and salmonella. Recent testing demonstrates elimination of PFAS (per- and polyfluoroalkyl substances) to below detection limits—addressing one of the most persistent environmental contaminants in biosolids and municipal waste streams.</p><h2 class=\"font-serif text-2xl text-[#1A3A2E] mt-6\">Carbon Removal Verification</h2><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">C-Link CORCs undergo independent third-party verification evaluating:</p><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">Feedstock sourcing and baseline emissions</p><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">Process lifecycle emissions and energy inputs</p><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">Carbon storage stability and permanence</p><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">Additionality and double-counting prevention</p><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">Certificates are validated on Puro.earth , which has been approved by the Integrity Council for the Voluntary Carbon Market (ICVCM) as an Eligible Carbon Crediting Programme, meeting institutional buyer requirements for transparency, traceability, and compliance with emerging carbon accounting standards.</p><p class=\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\">CORC Differentiation: Carbon removal certificates represent physical CO2 extracted from the atmosphere and stored long-term, distinct from avoidance-style offsets that prevent future emissions. This distinction matters increasingly as regulatory frameworks and corporate climate commitments require demonstrated removals rather than avoided emissions.</p></div><div class=\"mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border-2 border-[#1A3A2E] px-7 py-3.5 text-sm font-medium text-[#1A3A2E] hover:bg-[#1A3A2E] hover:text-white transition-all\" href=\"/case-studies\">View Related Case Studies</a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-[#F7FAF8] border-t border-gray-100\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-6\"><div><p class=\"text-[#52B788] text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase mb-2\">Impact Growth Labs</p><h3 class=\"font-serif text-2xl text-[#1A3A2E]\">Building alongside founders from day zero.</h3></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[#2D6A4F] font-medium hover:gap-3 transition-all shrink-0\" href=\"/portfolio\">Explore full portfolio <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main></div><footer class=\"bg-[#0F1A14] text-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12\"><div class=\"md:col-span-1\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-serif text-xl mb-4\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#52B788] text-[#0F1A14] text-sm font-bold\">IG</span>Impact Growth Labs</a><p class=\"text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-[220px]\">Backing founders who build a better world.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-white/40 mb-4\">Studio</h3><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li><a class=\"text-sm text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/portfolio\">Portfolio</a></li><li><a