 traditionally create methane emissions, fire hazards, and disposal costs—and convert them into stable carbon storage and regenerative soil inputs.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\",\"children\":[\"Each ton of material processed generates independently verified Carbon Removal Certificates (CORCs) representing permanent CO2 removal, plus nutrient-rich growing media for agricultural markets. This dual-output model addresses converging needs in waste management, climate accountability, and soil regeneration.\"]}],[\"$\",\"h2\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"font-serif text-2xl text-[#1A3A2E] mt-6\",\"children\":[\"The Technology: MicroSnap Process\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\",\"children\":[\"C-Link's Terrestrial Storage utilizes MicroSnap's carbon preservation technology—an advanced microbial process that stabilizes organic carbon at ambient temperature through controlled biological activity.\"]}],[\"$\",\"h3\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-lg text-[#1A3A2E] mt-4\",\"children\":[\"Verified Performance Metrics:\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"6\",{\"className\":\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\",\"children\":[\"\",[\"$\",\"strong\",\"1\",{\"children\":\"Energy efficiency\"}],\"\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"7\",{\"className\":\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\",\"children\":[\"Produces biochar-equivalent carbon storage using approximately one-tenth the energy of thermal pyrolysis\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"8\",{\"className\":\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\",\"children\":[\"\",[\"$\",\"strong\",\"1\",{\"children\":\"Mass retention\"}],\"\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"9\",{\"className\":\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\",\"children\":[\"Preserves 95-97% of starting material mass, maximizing both carbon capture and product yield\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"10\",{\"className\":\"text-[#0F1A14]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg\",\"children\":[\"\",[\"$\",\"strong\",\"1\",{\